1. *Baci* ga u vodu! (Throw him in the water!)
2. On je *bačen* u zatvor. (He was thrown in prison.)
3. Ona je *bačena* u depresiju. (She was thrown into depression.)
4. *Bacila* je kamu u rijeku. (She threw a stone in the river.)
5. Njegov glas je *bačen* na sve strane. (His voice was thrown in all directions.)
6. *Baci* oko na to! (Take a look at it!)